This world is a yakiniku set meal! Po----
shakarikishakari, work hard, manbo! This is my way
of life, po----
Hello. Are you Kokori, the supervisor here?

Uhuhuhu. Hey, try eating this. It'll make you
fly!!! Uhuhuhuhu

Ah! I've found an intruder! Teacher! Is this
person a bad guy?! Yes, that's right!

Ah! Who might you be?! We're sorry! We're sorry!
We're sorry! We're sorry!

The supervisor Kokori has become mentally unstable
due to drug addiction and can't speak properly
anymore.

To be honest, it's not okay. Could it be that
you're a messenger from Lady Dorothea? We haven't
heard from her in a while...

That's right. I was asked to do it. But there's
someone else, right? A magical girl? Um, the
person called Rudia.

Yes, Rudia went to search for a way to treat
Kokori's drug addiction, but she hasn't come back
yet.

So that's how it is. Well then, I'll report this
to Dorothea. I wonder if there's anything I should
bring with me?

Ah, then please take this! It's the observation
data that was compiled when Kokori was still
normal.
I understand. I hope Rudia returns soon...

This world is a yakiniku set meal! Po----
shakarikishakari, work hard, manbo! This is my way
of life, po----

From coordinate point 10324.5... -786.56, there's
a response this time... The change from last time
is... umm, the calculation formula is...
different... mumble mumble.

First of all, is the fire itself a type of flame
that has no effect on demons...? No, that can't be
true... The sample I collected should have been a
normal flame... Mumbling to oneself.
Are you okay? Is it an enemy attack!?

Run...! Kokori has turned into a demon... into a
demon...

Fshururururu~... Tobuzo... Tobuzo...! Collect and
see...!

Hey, I've been telling you that it's dangerous.
I'm Rosia... And you are...

I'm Konoha. I heard about you from Rosia, the
contact person.

Guh! The demons are multiplying one after another!
We'll talk later! Let's exterminate them!

Alright, I'll leave it to you, Kokori... If you've
turned into a demon, there's no other choice...!

It seems Rosia has been taken care of. Is everyone
okay?

Haa... haa... I'm sorry, but we're safe... The
researchers from Lolimon are also unharmed.
Phew! We thought we were going to die!

Well then... why did Kokori turn into a demon
again...

It seemed like symptoms of drug addiction, but
actually, it seems that was a precursor to
demonization.

That's right. The demons who don't like this
surveillance tower are releasing miasma. But
thanks to the barrier, this place is safe...

Maybe the barrier is weakening. It might be better
for the researchers to leave here early.

Is the barrier you're talking about the same as
the barrier pillars? Are they located in this
tower?

The barrier pillars are not here. They are all
located in the Crimson Bloodline Ruins and
distribute the power of the barrier from there.

I see, so they're located in a different place. It
would be better to confirm this. I'll report this
to Dorothea for now.

Understood. I will leave this tower with the
researchers and head to Lady Dorothea later.

Hey! Are you okay? Ugh... I can't do this alone...
We have no choice but to retreat for now.
